      "content": "Exactly. I feel like a ghost. Like I'm just a hollow shell performing a role that doesn't exist anymore. Everyone looks at me and sees a scientist, but there's nothing inside. The \"me\" that mattered is dead. How can someone even keep going when the core of who they are has just... evaporated?",
